(1862, 1, '2016-08-13 09:06:30', '2016-08-13 09:06:30', 'Ashika Prasai is a young student in Sydney, Australia. She has been in Sydney for 8 years pursuing the studies of nursing. Ashika grew up in the Jhapa, Nepal seeing her mother involved in the help making to the people in need in the neighbor, she started to envision of doing something to help in the society. Like mother, Maya Prasai, young Ashika has been raising scholarships for the needy students in Nepal’s villages. She has raised scholarships for 25 students in Dolpa in 2015 from Nepali’s diaspora in Australia. Personally, she has contributed for 5 students in Dolpa with Sadbhaw Scholarships.', 'Ashika Prasai', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'subash', '', '', '2016-09-03 16:06:14', '2016-09-03 16:06:14', '', 0, 'http://localhost/sadbhaw/?post_type=leader&#038;p=1862', 0, 'leader', '', 0),
